  "description": {
    "zh": "只剩下最后一类武器了，你兴奋吗？我建议你这次囤积点弹药，这次我不会给你任何备用装备了，明白吗？无意冒犯，但你知道，我也只是个商人，你也不会给我任何免费的东西，对吧？我就是这么想的。\n\n总之，责任在召唤！机枪可以是处理你的工作的绝佳工具，但你知道怎么回事……“车的好坏取决于司机”或类似的话。这些东西也很重，所以做一些训练会是明智之举，但这由你决定。",
    "en": "Only one class of weapons left, are you excited? I suggest you stock up on ammo this time, I won't be handing over any spare gear for you this time, you got that? No offense but you know, I'm also just a business man, you wouldn't give me any free stuff either, would you? That's what I thought.\n\nAnyway, duty is calling! Machine guns can be excellent tools to take care of your work, but you know how it goes... \"The car is only as good as it's driver\" or something like that. These things are very heavy too, so doing some training would be a smart move, but that is your call."
  },
